        Creates plot A/C equivalent stresses input.
        Parameters:
        stress - A/C equivalent stress.
        elementType - Element type.
        stressComponent - Stress component.
        mission - Fatigue mission.
        interpolate - True to interpolate elements without stresses.
        onegLC - 1G load case.
        dpLC - Delta-p load case.
        vgLC - Vertical gust load case.
        refStressComp - Reference stress component.
        dataSource - Interpolation data source option.
        beamExtrusion - BEAM element extrusion width.
        rodExtrusion - ROD element extrusion width.
        opacity - Element opacity.
        outlines - True if element outlines should be drawn.
        contour - Plot contour option.
